org.jetel.graph

Enum JobType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JobType>
      • org.jetel.graph.JobType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<JobType>

    public enum JobType
extends java.lang.Enum<JobType>
    This enumeration represents various kind of jobs from clover engine family. For now only ETL graph and jobflow types are considered. Each graph has specified its jobType, TransformationGraph#getJobType(). Job type is defined in *.grf file as an XML attribute of top level 'Graph' element.
